## Getting Started
### bash
```bash
python ./cellniche/main.py --config ./configs/xxx.yaml

```
### python
```python
import cellniche

# Parse arguments from a YAML config
opts = cellniche.parse_args([
    "--config", "configs/xxx.yaml"
])
# Run training/inference
cellniche.main(opts)

```

